Pomaličku.

6
00:00:35,360 --> 00:00:38,100
Mohla by sis zranit krk.

7
00:00:39,660 --> 00:00:40,700
Seo Jung, není ti nic?

8
00:00:41,330 --> 00:00:42,400
Promiň.

9
00:00:43,130 --> 00:00:44,130
Kdo jste?

10
